  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Petz Rescue: Ocean Sanctuary is an adventure game in which players manage a dolphin sanctuary for displaced or wounded ocean animals. Players complete various tasks and participate in mini-games, while learning about the plight of endangered species. Tasks/mini-games include tending to the wounds of dolphins, feeding dolphins, preparing medicine, and locating lost animals.",
